{"tid":131254,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬國斯：葛斯再係咁 就要踢中超！","createTime":"2017-02-23T02:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T05:38:28.000Z","uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b131efd77dc3af59eb4561e1fdf8b5be54298212","tid":131254,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:52:24.000Z","msg":"自於2014年世界盃決賽為德國一箭定江山以來，馬里奧葛斯(圖)愈踢愈沉，今季重返多蒙特仍未見起色，名宿馬圖斯對此表示：「離開拜仁之後，又要離開多蒙特？國外的頂級球會對他已不感興趣，如他在多蒙特無法立足而又想保持現有薪酬，他只能去中國，雖然那是可憐的。」"},{"pid":"e7f19e5b411f0acea508c8ab0dbf94cf3d7dad5e","tid":131254,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:53:54.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"8c3b38eacb02407ced7bf16b445f1f178b7c4803","tid":131254,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:56:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a26368fb2ca898ea599d8d48c0ebef8d68d76ad","tid":131254,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/105658_b33923f3b8eb50cb67d9bb2d9f05dd04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F105658_b33923f3b8eb50cb67d9bb2d9f05dd04.jpg&h=087ef115&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"750efa4125fd595964a5b25d5973931047c733e4","tid":131254,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"同港女一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34bedb9b2de5a2ec58bfa43aef390b12a7c3ddea","tid":131254,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"背叛我地利物浦係冇好下場"},{"pid":"6e202f565e930a6a1f0f375965521b541ae194e1","tid":131254,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:58:57.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 有利物浦唔踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793